body.p:
Our curve-net-based approach has the following merits:


the garments dressed on a reference human model can be transferred onto a target human model by reconstructing the garment geometry on the feature curve-net of the target human model;

the garments on a dressed human model can be interactively edited by altering the feature curve-net;

our approach supports directly fitting 3D garment models (without reference human model) onto 3D individual human models.
